{"id":1660,"date":"2020-10-08T11:09:17","date_gmt":"2020-10-08T11:09:17","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/?p=1660"},"modified":"2021-07-13T10:01:19","modified_gmt":"2021-07-13T10:01:19","slug":"chatbots-development-for-airline-industry","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/chatbots-development-for-airline-industry","title":{"rendered":"How Chatbots Are Reshaping The Future Of Airline Industry?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Technology and innovations helping the travel industry to re-shape their services and advance their relations with end-users by providing interactive and great user experience. Many <a href=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/how-chatbot-can-boost-travel-industries\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">travel companies face competition<\/a> from different areas, as travelers want to be more connected and empowered and are increasingly seeking digital engagement with greater transparency.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">From instant information to booking flight tickets; chatbots have introduced themselves as forward-thinking and a capable method to enhancing the experience of travelers.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What Exactly is a Chatbot?<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A chatbot is a computer program that can initiate a conversation just like humans. In technical terms, A chatbot is a computer program that simulates a human-like conversation with the user; using technologies like artificial intelligence and machine learning. A chatbot relies on natural language processing to understand the human language. Artificial intelligence and machine learning on the other hand help in providing intelligent responses to the user.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/why-80-of-businesses-are-approaching-chatbots-in-2020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Chatbots helps business owners in streamlining their business processes<\/a> and enhancing their customer relationships as it provides different types of ways to treat their customers in a better manner.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/jcR4V477XGU\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">\ufeff<\/span><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">\ufeff<\/span><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">\ufeff<\/span><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">\ufeff<\/span><span data-mce-type=\"bookmark\" style=\"display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;\" class=\"mce_SELRES_start\">\ufeff<\/span><\/iframe><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Statistics<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At a compound annual growth rate (<a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Compound_annual_growth_rate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CAGR<\/a>) of 29.7% the chatbot market size is projected to grow from $2.6 billion in 2019 to $9.4 billion by 2024.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The chatbot market is growing at a CAGR of 9% in the Asia Pacific followed by North America at 31.2 % CAGR\u00a0 and Europe with a 30.4% CAGR. In the customer service segment, a chatbot is expected to be the fastest-growing market segment between 2019-2026 with a CAGR of 31.6%. <\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">82% of consumers claim that instant responses to their questions are very important when contacting brands.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">57% of executives said that chatbots bring significant ROI with minimal effort.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">55% of consumers are willing to interact with a business via messaging apps to solve a problem.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Businesses spend over $1.3 trillion per year to address customer requests. Chatbots could help to reduce that cost by 30%.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">74% of Millennials said their perception of brand improves if the company responds to their social media inquiries via chatbot.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Benefits of Chatbots in the Airline Industry:<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Customer Care:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> A chatBot is a conversational agent that can interact with a user. Chatbots are quick to respond to customer questions and can help solve their problems like timings, charges, and booking tickets. Questions may not get answered in a long &amp; regular live chat where users speak to a customer service professional. This further can lead your business to lose loyal customers who grew frustrated waiting for assistance.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Reservation Agents:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> with the help of flight bots; Individuals, groups and business travelers plan and organize their flight reservations from getting flight information to booking flights.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Convert Visitors Into Buyers:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> With the help of chatbots, you can show your visitors special discounts or coupon codes just before they leave your site. These people were about to leave forever and not spend more time but ChatBot can save them!<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1867 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/chatbot_for_airline.jpg\" alt=\"Chatbot for Airline\" width=\"900\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/chatbot_for_airline.jpg 900w, https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/chatbot_for_airline-300x167.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/chatbot_for_airline-768x427.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><b>Cost-Effective:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> By using AI and chatbot technology businesses can save more than 29% expense from the original cost of human professionals. Bots help to lessen the service cost and speed up the response time without agent involvement.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Data Access (Record all the chat history):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> With help of Chatbot open data in our Unified API already helping to provide live customers reports to quickly and easily data access the information.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>User Need Analysis:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Flight bots can understand the user\u2019s queries and analyze customer requirements that help businesses to make their services more effective in a perfect manner. One chatbot is enough to solve the queries of many users and avoid the case of customer dissatisfaction.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Increase revenue:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Increase the dollar value of each of your customers by converting and selling more often. The chatbot can engage with customers in a user-friendly manner to provide them with quick and relevant responses.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Get Your Airline Business On Board With Chatbot<\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Relationships with customers increase as services become more personalized. Thus you don&#8217;t only need chatbot support to satisfy a customer. You also need a well-authorized organization that can develop a chatbot for your brand according to your needs. Chatbots are significantly simpler and faster to build than applications. Aryavrat Infotech can help you with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/bot-development\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Chatbot Development Services<\/a> by creating a powerful chatbot for your brand that will take your Airline business to a higher altitude of customer service.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https:\/\/schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"BlogPosting\",\n  \"mainEntityOfPage\": {\n    \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n    \"@id\": \"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/chatbots-development-for-airline-industry\"\n  },\n  \"headline\": \"How Chatbots Are Reshaping The Future Of Airline Industry?\",\n  \"description\": \"Aryavrat Infotech helps you with Chatbot Development Services for your brand that will take your Airline business to a higher altitude.\",\n  \"image\": [\n    \"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/AI-Chatbot-1024x576-1.png\",\n    \"https:\/\/youtu.be\/jcR4V477XGU\",\n    \"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/10\/chatbot_for_airline.jpg\"\n  ],  \n  \"author\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Aryavrat Infotech Inc.\"\n  },  \n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Aryavrat Infotech Inc.\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https:\/\/www.aryausa.com\/images\/arya-logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"datePublished\": \"2020-10-08\",\n  \"dateModified\": \"2021-07-02\"\n}\n<\/script><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Aryavrat Infotech helps you with Chatbot Development Services for your brand that will take your Airline business to a higher altitude.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1876,"comment_status":"open","